{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji23.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给陈理昆“的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给陈瑾昆\"的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年7月13日）瑾老同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大示敬悉。你们一家安于农村生活，闻之甚慰。立法工作是一新部门，得兄主持，日起有功，是大好事。时局如兄所料，人民战争是发展的；惟艰苦奋斗，尚须付以数年时间。我们在此均好，勿以为念。谨复。顺候大安!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月十三日[1]陈瑾昆，当时任中共中央法律委员会委员。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":7,"day":13}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":132,"page_end":132},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"人民战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}